{"tid":2344464,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"劉康: 列斯市議會發聲明撐香港人","createTime":"2020-12-28T17:56:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T18:50:39.000Z","uid":240362,"like":175,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"6091beafa798d0dec15f3dec3e3d770815064f5a","tid":2344464,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T17:56:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/133512297_182682683510991_1011958246897638398_o.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=7nQALNe8WS4AX-XhgT0&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-2.xx&amp;oh=c278ae8039ea8d504d83fcc6d0ef420d&amp;oe=60103ECA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F133512297_182682683510991_1011958246897638398_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3D7nQALNe8WS4AX-XhgT0%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-2.xx%26oh%3Dc278ae8039ea8d504d83fcc6d0ef420d%26oe%3D60103ECA&h=733a6872&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n列斯市議會發聲明撐香港人 | Leeds City Council Has Issued a Statement Supporting Hongkongers<br />\n<br />\n身為香港人，喺英國既然可以呼吸自由空氣，享受言論自由，就有責任將香港人為自由奮鬥嘅聲音傳遍英國，包括英國嘅社區同城市。我同英國港僑協會成員積極聯絡列斯市議會，同埋喺今個月從列斯市議會領袖Judith Blake CBE收到，列斯市議會關於香港嘅聲明。<br />\n<br />\n列斯市議會篇聲明提到，中國國安法妨礙香港人嘅權利同自由，亦都違反咗英中聯合聲明。聲明亦話，列斯市議會致力確保列斯社區安全，同埋藉此支持香港人。<br />\n<br />\n列斯係英國大城市，而且亦都專於金融業。得到列斯市議會支持，對香港人嚟講係非常重要。我非常感激，列斯市議會願意為香港人嘅自由而發聲。未來我會繼續團結英國民主勢力，務求令更多英國人認知香港人權狀況，同埋爭取更多英國人支持香港人。<br />\n<br />\nThis month, I and a member of Hongkongers in Britain have received a &ldquo;Statement from Leeds City Council on Hong Kong&rdquo; from Leeds City Council leader Cllr. Judith Blake CBE. I am really grateful to Leeds City Council for speaking out for Hongkongers&rsquo; freedoms. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HoncquesLausIsWanted/photos/a.124683152644278/182682680177658\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHoncquesLausIsWanted%2Fphotos%2Fa.124683152644278%2F182682680177658&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9UzxwX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=b1c9d2af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HoncquesLausIsWanted/photos/a.124683152644278/182682680177658</a>"},{"pid":"0d111e5a7d04c9251cf622f9187ad9a44e9e93d4","tid":2344464,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T17:57:54.000Z","msg":"除夕唔好倒數，唔好叫新年快樂，用悲鳴聲代替<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2342091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2342091</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1505763bfa3aad03eea85d1109e48a0033dbc74a","tid":2344464,"uid":13395,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T17:58:07.000Z","msg":"列斯聯係咪係列斯市？"},{"pid":"1ef5a0294d9a42ba30232f66545fa8febbb6caa8","tid":2344464,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T17:58:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be638cf5992e757bd5a4913810e91785fd9b185","tid":2344464,"uid":306914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T17:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f148ecd053f29f5bea0389bc4bba68c42db298c6","tid":2344464,"uid":286985,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T17:59:20.000Z","msg":"《借位share》<br />\n第三篇： 以加拿大人為榮者的敘述<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wiheUoDAhWU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwiheUoDAhWU&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9UzxwX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=e176490a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wiheUoDAhWU</a><br />\n&ldquo; 我開始明白到在中國發生的事情，並非與我無關. &rdquo;<br />\n在加拿大國土居然受到中國共產黨的威脅！？<br />\n聽聽這位加拿大人現身說法.<br />\n<br />\n